Description: An R package to analyze adverse events in clinical trials using the 'metalite' data structure.
  The R package simplified the workflow to create production ready table, listing and figures discussed in the 
  Chpater 7 and Chapter 8 of the R for Clinical Study Reports and Submission book (https://r4csr.org/). 
